{"tid":222280,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有聽開陳潔儀？","createTime":"2017-04-29T11:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:06:14.000Z","uid":591,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4ab553d9310456f8e57940f750d1e025bb8d68","tid":222280,"uid":591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"睇完妙手仁心之後就係youtube搵林保怡d歌聽<br />\n無意中聽到「不知不覺」<br />\n覺得好好聽 <br />\n之後再聽埋陳潔儀d歌<br />\n就開始沉船啦<br />\n<br />\n麻醉 分享孤獨 藍色幽默 心痛 心動<br />\n來夜方長 等了又等 揭曉 喜歡你 失蹤<br />\n好多都好正<br />\n好鐘意聽佢唱粵語歌<br />\n<br />\n最新隻碟「天堂邊緣」都好高質<br />\n<br />\n沉得太遲，錯過左上年著迷演唱會<br />\n唔知會幾時再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JX_G__awr6I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJX_G__awr6I&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ec4da8e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JX_G__awr6I</a><br />\n呢條片勁正勁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca84507decf90927616015be4e13d69814063ff5","tid":222280,"uid":591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b198393db73ec093fc418d611d7e873fd0e6d7","tid":222280,"uid":90128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"佢首喜歡你係正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f538428b9af2484876f50b3a3f75b2c53de00fa","tid":222280,"uid":73463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi